Package: nucleos
Title: Central Bank of Brazil Inflation Cores
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Vítor",
           family = "Wilher",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "analisemacro.cloud@gmail.com")
Description: Calculates the inflation cores and other analytical series derived
    from the IPCA, following the consolidated methodology published by the
    Central Bank of Brazil in Technical Note 57 (December 2025). Covers the 22
    series published in the SGS, from January 1991 onwards, spanning the five
    IPCA structures.
